snippet.title: Street Fighter III 3rd Strike playthrough (PS2)
snippet.description: Playthrough with Ken. In Japan, 3rd Strike was released as a stand-alone game, whilst America got a better deal as Capcom released Street Fighter Anniversary Collection, which had this game along with Hyper Street Fighter II. Meanwhile Europe...got nothing, as 3rd Strike was never released for the PS2 there.
